T02TD2761E:139a-0: @139a * // dpal thugs rje chen po lus kyi 'khor lo chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2761E:139a-1: 'jig rten mgon gyi man ngag gis //
T02TD2761E:139a-2: sngags 'chang rgyal po rang gi lus //
T02TD2761E:139a-4: sems kyis lha bcu gcag bcas bsgom //
T02TD2761E:139a-5: rtsi yis lcags gong gser bzhin du //
T02TD2761E:139a-6: phung po ye shes spyod yul bsgyur //
T02TD2761E:139a-7: de dbus snying gi 'dab bzhi dang //
T02TD2761E:139a-8: yan lag drug rtsibs mkhas pas bsgom //
T02TD2761E:139a-10: hr'i:/ kun gzhi rnam dag lhun gyis grub //
T02TD2761E:139a-11: 'jig rten dbang phyug gangs ri'i mdog / ting 'dzin mchog gis mnyam gzhag pa //
T02TD2761E:139a-12: bag chags ma lus bcom pa'o //
T02TD2761E:139a-14: gti mug rnam dag rnam mi rtog / gti mug rdo rje nam mkha'i mdog / dus gsum bde gshegs chos ston pa //
T02TD2761E:139a-15: thibs po ma lus gtan bcom pa'o //
T02TD2761E:139a-17: 'dod chags rnam dag bde pa che //
T02TD2761E:139a-18: 'dod chags rdo rje zla ba'i mdog / rdo rje dril bu bsnol 'dzin pa //
T02TD2761E:139a-19: gdung ba ma lus gtan bcom pa'o //
T02TD2761E:139a-21: zhe sdang rnam dag 'od gsal ba //
T02TD2761E:139a-22: zhes sdang rdo rje me lce'i mdog /'bar ba'i phyag rgya sdigs mdzub bsgyings//
T02TD2761E:139b-0: @139b 'khrug pa ma lus gtan bcom pa'o //
T02TD2761E:139b-1: a'a:kun rtog rnam dag gya gyu med //
T02TD2761E:139b-2: kun rtog rdo rje aindra'i mdog /'bar ba'i gar gyis rnam par rol //
T02TD2761E:139b-3: 'du byed ma lus gtan bcom pa'o //
T02TD2761E:139b-4: 'di dag ni dbus nas brtsams te shar la sogs pa'i 'dab ma bzhi'i ge sar la bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD2761E:139b-5: de nas 'gro ba drug gi rnam par dag pa dgod par bya ste /
T02TD2761E:139b-6: lha rigs rnam dga' chi 'pho med //
T02TD2761E:139b-7: dbang po rdo rje gur kum mdog / me tog phreng ba'i chun po 'dzin //
T02TD2761E:139b-8: dregs pa ma lus spangs pa'o //
T02TD2761E:139b-10: lha min rnam dag 'khrug pa med //
T02TD2761E:139b-11: drag po rdo rje rgya skyegs mdog / ral gri dang ni 'khor lo 'dzin //
T02TD2761E:139b-12: phrag dog ma lus kun spangs pa'o //
T02TD2761E:139b-14: mi dbang rnam dag brel por sa med //
T02TD2761E:139b-15: dbang phyug rdo rje rdza gsar mdog / rdo rje dang ni dril bu 'dzin //
T02TD2761E:139b-16: rnam par g-yengs pa kun spangs pa'o //
T02TD2761E:139b-18: dud 'gro rnam dag blun rmongs med //
T02TD2761E:139b-19: seng ge rdo rje du ba'i mdog / dgra sta dang ni dbyig pa 'dzin //
T02TD2761E:139b-20: bag med btul ba kun spyangs pa'o //
T02TD2761E:139b-22: yi dgas rnam dag ser sna med //
T02TD2761E:139b-23: gshin rje rdo rje char sprin mdog //
T02TD2761E:139b-24: thod pa dang ni zhags pa 'dzin //
T02TD2761E:139b-25: 'jungs pa'i sreng pa kun spangs pa'o //
T02TD2761E:139b-27: dmyal ba rnam dag tsha grang med //
T02TD2761E:139b-28: 'jigs skyob rdo rje byi ru'i mdog / bum pa dang ni lhung bzed 'dzin //
T02TD2761E:139b-29: mi bzad yang kun spangs pa'o //
T02TD2761E:139b-31: 'di dag ni mgo nas brtsams te g-yas la sogs pa'i rtsibs drug gi lte bar bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD2761E:139b-32: dam tshig lus dang sems la ni //
T02TD2761E:139b-33: ye shes sku dang thugs bcug nas /
T02TD2761E:139b-34: sa bon gsung gi yi ge bzlas //
T02TD2761E:139b-36: thugs rje chen po lus kyi 'khor lo 'bar ba rdzogs so//
